             was indicted for <rs id="t17920215-12-off62" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17920215-12-off62" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17920215-12-off62" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17920215-12-cd63" type="crimeDate">14th day of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17920215-12-off62 t17920215-12-cd63"></join> last, two pair of women's leather slippers, value 5 s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17920215-12-victim214" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Bloomfield
                  <interp inst="t17920215-12-victim214" type="surname" value="Bloomfield"></interp>
